---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-stone bg-mist">
  <div class="container-pm py-12">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.5fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]">
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5" aria-label="GameStatiq">
          <img src="/brand/gamestatiq-icon.svg" alt="" class="h-7 w-7" width="28" height="28" />
          <span class="text-[17px] font-semibold tracking-tight-2">
            Game<span class="font-bold text-signal">Statiq</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-xs text-sm text-slate">
          Sport stats platforma — měřte každou hru, od amatérského zápasu až po ligové finále.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Produkt</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/#features" class="text-graphite hover:text-ink">Funkce</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#how" class="text-graphite hover:text-ink">Jak to funguje</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#pricing" class="text-graphite hover:text-ink">Cena</a></li>
          <li><a href="/liga" class="text-graphite hover:text-ink">Liga &amp; kluby</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Společnost</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/#contact" class="text-graphite hover:text-ink">Kontakt</a></li>
          <li><a href="/o-nas" class="text-graphite hover:text-ink">O nás</a></li>
          <li><a href="mailto:hello@gamestatiq.com" class="text-graphite hover:text-ink">hello@gamestatiq.com</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Právní</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/podminky" class="text-graphite hover:text-ink">Podmínky</a></li>
          <li><a href="/soukromi" class="text-graphite hover:text-ink">Ochrana údajů</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-3 border-t border-stone pt-6 text-xs text-slate sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
      <p>© {year} GameStatiq. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p class="font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.12em]">Measure every play</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
